  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      vitamin D has great role in bone regenration and soft tissue health. in the past periodontal
      regeneration was performed using bone graft and barrier membrane
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      there was no previous studies used the locally injected vitamin d in periodontal
      regeneration. therefore, we intended to study the effect of locally injected vitamin D in
      peridoontal regerneration in comparison with the conventional surgical technique
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
